*主要編曲人：[[高世章|高世章]]、[[Iskandar_Ismail|Iskandar Ismail]]、[[Sydney_Tan|Sydney Tan]]、[[吳慶隆|吳慶隆]]、[[Robert_Seng|Robert Seng]]
